data.text: And I would take magazine cutouts and tape them all over my wall. It was a collage of pics ranging from tiny cutouts to big poster sizes. I cried when people at school started clowning on her over the lip sync fiasco at SNL. Like legit bawled. I was so depressed

You guys don’t even understand. If you thought any of my other celebrity obsessions were bad, this one takes the fucken cake. The summer before starting middle school I discovered Ashlee and my life was never the same. I had a spongebob wallet that I wrote Ashlee Simpson all over
